### Users API Manual Test Collection

@base = http://localhost:3000/api/users

### Registrar usuario
POST {{base}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Juan Perez",
  "email": "juan{{timestamp}}@mail.com",
  "username": "juan{{timestamp}}",
  "password": "Password!1",
  "profile_image": "https://example.com/avatar.png",
  "favorite_instrument": 0
}
###

### Login usuario
POST {{base}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userOrEmail": "juan{{timestamp}}",
  "password": "Password!1"
}
###

### Obtener todos los usuarios (rol comun_user filtrado internamente)
GET {{base}}/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Obtener usuario por id
GET {{base}}/id/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Obtener usuario por email
GET {{base}}/email/juan{{timestamp}}@mail.com
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Actualizar usuario
PUT {{base}}/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "full_name": "Juan P. Actualizado"
}
###

### Borrado l√≥gico usuario
DELETE {{base}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

